# 97. al-qadr: The Majesty

<span id="an_097_001">1</span> Lo! We revealed it on the Night of
Predestination.

<span id="an_097_002">2</span> Ah, what will convey unto thee what the
Night of Power is!

<span id="an_097_003">3</span> The Night of Power is better than a
thousand months.

<span id="an_097_004">4</span> The angels and the Spirit descend
therein, by the permission of their Lord, with all decrees.

<span id="an_097_005">5</span> (The night is) Peace until the rising of
the dawn.

